---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { Calendar, CheckCircle, Clock, ArrowRight } from 'lucide-react';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Schedule Your Basecamp Session | Climb.Coach"
  description="Schedule your initial Basecamp coaching session with Climb.Coach after completing your payment."
>
  <section class="relative py-16 md:py-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-cambridge-blue/10 to-white">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-15 bg-[url('/topography-pattern.svg')] bg-repeat"></div>
    <div class="container relative z-10 mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center bg-mountain-green/30 rounded-full py-1.5 px-4 mb-6 shadow-md">
          <CheckCircle className="h-4 w-4 text-blue-mell mr-2" />
          <span class="text-xs font-medium text-dark-slate">PAYMENT SUCCESSFUL</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-charcoal mb-6">
          Thank You For Your Purchase
        </h1>
        
        <p class="text-lg text-dark-slate/90 mb-10">
          Your investment in your growth journey is confirmed. The next step is to schedule your first coaching session (Basecamp) at a time that works best for you.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-mountain-green/30 mb-10">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <Calendar className="h-10 w-10 text-blue-mell mr-3" />
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-charcoal">Schedule Your Basecamp Session</h2>
          </div>
          
          <p class="text-dark-slate/90 mb-8">
            Use our scheduling system below to select the perfect time for your initial Basecamp coaching session.
          </p>
          
          <div class="mb-6">
            <!-- Setmore Scheduling Widget -->
            <div id="setmore-embed" class="w-full max-w-xl mx-auto overflow-hidden rounded-lg shadow-lg">
              <iframe 
                id="setmore-frame"
                src="https://climbcoach.setmore.com/services/38ebbc66-2899-4cf4-9ec4-26d6c1e5c4a3" 
                scrolling="yes" 
                width="100%" 
                height="750px" 
                frameborder="0"
                class="rounded-lg"
                style="min-height:750px; overflow:auto;"
              ></iframe>
            </div>
          </div>
          
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-mountain-green/20 flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="bg-blue-mell/10 rounded-full p-3 mb-4">
              <Clock className="h-6 w-6 text-blue-mell" />
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-heading font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">Session Duration</h3>
            <p class="text-dark-slate/80 text-center text-sm">
              Your Basecamp session will last 45 minutes, giving us ample time to dive deep.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-mountain-green/20 flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="bg-blue-mell/10 rounded-full p-3 mb-4">
              <Calendar className="h-6 w-6 text-blue-mell" />
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-heading font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">Availability</h3>
            <p class="text-dark-slate/80 text-center text-sm">
              Select from available times across different time zones for your convenience.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-mountain-green/20 flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="bg-blue-mell/10 rounded-full p-3 mb-4">
              <CheckCircle className="h-6 w-6 text-blue-mell" />
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-heading font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">Confirmation</h3>
            <p class="text-dark-slate/80 text-center text-sm">
              You'll receive an email confirmation with all details and calendar invite.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 p-6 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl shadow-md border border-mountain-green/30">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-charcoal mb-4">What to Expect Next</h2>
          <ul class="text-left text-dark-slate/90 space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <ArrowRight className="h-4 w-4 text-blue-mell mt-1 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" />
              <span>After scheduling, you'll receive a welcome email with pre-session materials</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <ArrowRight className="h-4 w-4 text-blue-mell mt-1 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" />
              <span>Your coach will connect with you via Google Meet at your scheduled time</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <ArrowRight className="h-4 w-4 text-blue-mell mt-1 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" />
              <span>Come prepared with any specific topics or challenges you'd like to address</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <ArrowRight className="h-4 w-4 text-blue-mell mt-1 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" />
              <span>You'll receive an invite to your coaching portal in Notion where you can chat with your coach and access session notes and action steps</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <ArrowRight className="h-4 w-4 text-blue-mell mt-1 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" />
              <span>Your coach will reach out to you shortly with more information about your journey</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-10 text-dark-slate/80">
          Questions about your booking? Contact us at <a href="mailto:support@climb.coach" class="text-blue-mell hover:underline">support@climb.coach</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>